OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1776330350
OL,3,CTwo sought over attempted arson attack
OL,4,Cat north London synagogue
OL,6,FAn investigation has been launched
OL,7,Fafter an attempted arson attack was
OL,8,Flaunched on a synagogue in north
OL,9,FLondon overnight.
OL,11,FPolice are looking for two suspects
OL,12,Fwho were wearing dark clothing and
OL,13,Fbalaclavas as they approached Finchley
OL,14,FReform Synagogue shortly after
OL,15,Fmidnight on Wednesday.
OL,17,FInvestigators say the pair threw two
OL,18,Fbottles, suspected to contain petrol,
OL,19,Fand a brick at the building in Fallow
OL,20,FCourt Avenue.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
