FL,306,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30502
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1776330350
OL,3,CTwo sought over attempted arson attack
OL,4,Cat north London synagogue
OL,6,FNeither bottle ignited and no damage
OL,7,Fwas reported and no one was injured,
OL,8,Fthe Metropolitan Police said.
OL,10,FNo arrests have been made yet and that
OL,11,Fthey are urgently trying to trace the
OL,12,Fsuspects.
OL,14,FThe road approaching the Finchley
OL,15,FReform Synagogue has been cordoned off
OL,16,Fby police .
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/12
