PN,30503
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1776330350
OL,3,CTwo sought over attempted arson attack
OL,4,Cat north London synagogue
OL,6,FIn a post on X, Labour MP for Finchley
OL,7,Fand Golders Green, Sarah Sackman
OL,8,Fwrote: "This morning, I became aware
OL,9,Fof an attempted arson attack at
OL,10,FFinchley Reform Synagogue overnight.
OL,12,F"Thankfully, no one has been hurt. I
OL,13,Fhave been at the synagogue, supporting
OL,14,Flocal residents and community leaders.
OL,16,F"This shocking attempt to harm a local
OL,17,Fsynagogue follows a series of alarming
OL,18,Fattacks on the Jewish community in
OL,19,FFinchley and Golders Green.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,306,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30504
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1776330350
OL,3,CTwo sought over attempted arson attack
OL,4,Cat north London synagogue
OL,6,F"As your local MP, and as a member of
OL,7,Fthe community, I refuse to allow this
OL,8,Fto become the 'new normal'.
OL,10,F"British Jews must be free to go about
OL,11,Ftheir lives without fear ` whether
OL,12,Ftaking their children to nursery or
OL,13,Fattending synagogue.
OL,15,F"We do not want to live behind ever
OL,16,Fhigher walls. I thank the CST and
OL,17,FMetropolitan Police for their quick
OL,18,Fand effective response.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,306,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30505
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1776330350
OL,3,CTwo sought over attempted arson attack
OL,4,Cat north London synagogue
OL,6,F"I will continue to raise the issues
OL,7,Fof antisemitism and security at the
OL,8,Fhighest levels in government to
OL,9,Fprotect our community."
OL,11,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,12,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,13,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,14,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,16,FDetective Chief Superintendent Luke
OL,17,FWilliams said: "We are aware of the
OL,18,Fsignificant concern that this incident
OL,19,Fwill cause in the community,
OL,20,Fparticularly in the wake of the arson
OL,21,Fattack in Golders Green last month.
OL,26,@yD@POU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,306,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30506
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1776330350
OL,3,CTwo sought over attempted arson attack
OL,4,Cat north London synagogue
OL,6,F"I would like to reassure the
OL,7,Fcommunity that we take incidents of
OL,8,Fthis nature extremely seriously and
OL,9,Fdetectives are working urgently to
OL,10,Fidentify the suspects.
OL,12,F"Residents can expect to see a
OL,13,Fheightened police presence in the area
OL,14,Fover the coming days. We have brought
OL,15,Fin additional officers and would urge
OL,16,Fanyone with concerns to speak to them."
OL,26,@nD@AOUtD@AOUxD@gO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
