PN,30507
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1776330350
OL,3,CTwo sought over attempted arson attack
OL,4,Cat north London synagogue
OL,6,FIn a statement on Wednesday, the
OL,7,FCommunity Security Trust (CST), a
OL,8,Fcharity that protect the British
OL,9,FJewish community, said the attack is
OL,10,Fbeing "treated as an antisemitic hate
OL,11,Fcrime".
OL,13,F"We are supporting the affected
OL,14,Flocation and are working closely with
OL,15,Fthe police as they investigate and
OL,16,Fseek to identify those responsible. We
OL,17,Furge anyone with information to
OL,18,Fcontact the police on 999 and then
OL,19,FCST."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
