PN,30508
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1776330350
OL,3,CTwo sought over attempted arson attack
OL,4,Cat north London synagogue
OL,6,FFranco Di Landro, 56, who is an
OL,7,Finterior gardener and lives close to
OL,8,Fthe synagogue, told the Press
OL,9,FAssociation: "I was lying on the sofa,
OL,10,Fwatching the TV, when all of a sudden,
OL,11,FI heard an almighty bang.
OL,13,F"It felt, sounded like a boulder had
OL,14,Fhit the floor, and it came from
OL,15,Foutside. I came outside but I couldn't
OL,16,Fsee nothing.
OL,18,F"But then this morning, when I woke
OL,19,Fup, I noticed a forensic van at the
OL,20,Fend of the road, and I thought 'oh,
OL,21,FChrist, that doesn't sound good'.
OL,26,@qD@NOUuD@AOUzD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,306,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30509
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1776330350
OL,3,CTwo sought over attempted arson attack
OL,4,Cat north London synagogue
OL,6,F"Then there was more and more police,
OL,7,Fthe road then cordoned off, and then
OL,8,Flooking on social media, I noticed
OL,9,Fthat there's been a fire mention about
OL,10,Ffire bomb in the synagogue. It is
OL,11,Fscary."
OL,13,FHe added: "We've been here since 2011.
OL,14,FIt's scary, though. I must say that,
OL,15,Fit's scary.
OL,17,F"You know, I only just live literally
OL,18,F30 metres away from the place, and to
OL,19,Fhear that a bomb, they tried to put a
OL,20,Ffire bomb in the building. That is
OL,21,Fscary."
OL,26,@nD@AOUsD@GO]uD@KOUyD@AOU}D@GO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/12
