OL,3,CTwo sought over attempted arson attack
OL,4,Cat north London synagogue
OL,6,FFinchley Church End Cllr Josh Mastin-
OL,7,FLee said the synagogue is "a pillar of
OL,8,Fthe community that deserves far
OL,9,Fbetter", adding "these attacks must
OL,10,Fend".
OL,12,FReacting to the incident, he said in a
OL,13,Fpost on X: "Yet another despicable
OL,14,Fattempt to target and intimidate
OL,15,FFinchley's Jewish community.
OL,17,F"I visited Finchley Reform Synagogue
OL,18,Ffor their Holocaust Memorial Day
OL,19,Fworkshop in January. A pillar of the
OL,20,Fcommunity that deserves far better.
OL,26,@oD@[OUqD@GO]qD@QOUrD@DO]uD@LOUyD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
