PN,30511
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1776330350
OL,3,CTwo sought over attempted arson attack
OL,4,Cat north London synagogue
OL,6,F"These attacks must end."
OL,8,FMayor of London Sir Sadiq Khan said:
OL,9,F"I'm grateful to the Met Police for
OL,10,Ftheir swift response to the appalling
OL,11,Fattempted arson attack at Finchley
OL,12,FReform Synagogue overnight.
OL,14,F"The incident is being treated as an
OL,15,Fantisemitic hate crime, and there is
OL,16,Fan increased police presence in place
OL,17,Fin the local area.
OL,19,F"While thankfully no-one was injured,
OL,20,Fthe Met are urging anyone with
OL,21,Finformation to come forward."
OL,26,@nD@AOUnD@YO]qD@AOUvD@AOU{D@AOU}D@]O]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G11/12
